'''[[:en:Non-governmental_organization|Kubungabunga]] inyamaswa''' bivuga imyitozo yo kurinda [[:en:Species|amoko]] y’inyamanswa n’aho atuye hagamijwe kubungabunga amoko y’ibinyabuzima cyangwa abaturage ndetse no kugarura, kurinda cyangwa kuzamura [[:en:Ecosystem|urusobe rw’ibinyabuzima]] . Ikibazo gikomeye kibangamiye inyamaswa zirimo [[:en:Habitat_destruction|gusenya aho gutura]], kwangirika, gucikamo ibice, gukoresha cyane, guhiga, guhumana n’imihindagurikire y’ikirere. [[Abishyize Hamwe Bashinzwe Kubungabunga Isi|IUCN]] ivuga ko amoko 27.000 y’ibisuzumwa afite ibyago byo kuzimira. Kwiyongera ku moko yose ariho, raporo y’umuryango w’abibumbye yo mu 2019 ivuga ku [[:en:Biodiversity|binyabuzima]] yashyize iyi mibare hejuru cyane ku bwoko bwa miliyoni. Birashimangirwa kandi ko umubare w’ibinyabuzima byiyongera ku isi birimo amoko yangiritse bigenda bicika. Kugira ngo ibyo bibazo bikemuke, habaye ingufu za leta ndetse n’amahanga mu kubungabunga inyamaswa zo ku isi. Amasezerano akomeye yo kubungabunga ibidukikije arimo Amasezerano yo mu 1973 [[Ubucuruzi Mpuzamahanga bw’Ibinyabuzima Bwenda Gucika|y’ubucuruzi mpuzamahanga ku bwoko bw’inyamaswa zo mu gasozi n’ibimera]] (CITES) [[:en:Convention_on_Biological_Diversity|n’amasezerano yo mu 1992 y’ibinyabuzima bitandukanye]] (CBD). <ref name=":62">https://www.cites.org/eng/disc/what.php</ref> <ref name=":72">https://www.cbd.int/history/default.shtml</ref> Hariho kandi imiryango myinshi [[:en:Non-governmental_organization|itegamiye kuri leta]] (ONG) igamije kubungabunga ibidukikije nko [[Ikigega Mpuzamahanga Gishinzwe Umutungo Kamere|kubungabunga ibidukikije]], [[Ikigega Mpuzamahanga Gishinzwe Umutungo Kamere|ikigega cy’ibinyabuzima ku isi]], ndetse no [[:en:Conservation_International|kubungabunga ibidukikije]] .

== Itotezwa  ku nyamaswa ==
[[Dosiye:Lacanja_burn_crop.JPG|alt=|thumb|275x275px|Ishyamba ryatwitse ubuhinzi mu majyepfo ya [[Megizike|Mexico]] .]]
[[:en:Habitat_destruction|Kurimbuka]] gutura bigabanya umubare wibinyabuzima bishobora guturamo. [[:en:Habitat_fragmentation|Gutandukana kw'imiturire]] bisenya inzira ikomeza guturamo, akenshi igabanya inyamaswa nini zo mu gasozi mo utuntu duto duto. <ref name=":12">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)</ref> [[:en:Habitat_loss|Gutakaza abantu gutura]] no gucikamo ibice nibyo bintu nyamukuru bigabanuka no kuzimangana. Ingero zingenzi zo gutakaza aho abantu batuye harimo gutema amashyamba, [[:en:Agricultural_expansion|kwagura ubuhinzi]], no [[:en:Urbanization|mumijyi]] . Kurimbuka kw'imiturire no gucikamo ibice birashobora kongera kwibasirwa n’ibinyabuzima byo mu gasozi mu kugabanya umwanya n’umutungo bahabwa no kongera amakimbirane n’abantu. Byongeye kandi, gusenya no gucamo ibice bitera ahantu hato. Ahantu hatuwe hashyigikira abaturage bake, kandi abaturage bake barashobora kuzimira. <ref name=":22">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780198783398</ref>

== Kurenza urugero /Overexploitation ==
[[:en:Overexploitation|Gukabya gukabya]] ni ugusarura inyamaswa n'ibimera ku kigero cyihuta kuruta ubushobozi bwubwoko. Mugihe gikunze guhuzwa no [[:en:Overfishing|Kuroba]] cyane, kurenza urugero birashobora gukoreshwa mumatsinda menshi arimo inyamaswa z’inyamabere, inyoni, amphibian, ibikururuka hasi, n'ibimera. <ref>https://www.nwf.org/Home/Educational-Resources/Wildlife-Guide/Threats-to-Wildlife/Overexploitation</ref> Akaga ko gukabya gukabije ni uko niba hafashwe abantu benshi cyane b'ubwoko, ubwo bwoko ntibushobora gukira. <ref>https://enviroliteracy.org/ecosystems/drivers-of-biodiversity-loss/overexploitation/</ref> Kurugero, kuroba cyane amafi yinyamaswa zo mu nyanja nka tuna na salmon mu kinyejana gishize byatumye igabanuka ry’amafi kimwe n’amafi. <ref name=":122">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)</ref> 

== Guhiga Inyamanswa ==
[[:en:Poaching|Guhiga]] [[:en:Wildlife_trading|ubucuruzi bw’inyamanswa]] butemewe n’iterabwoba rikomeye ku bwoko bumwe na bumwe, cyane cyane bugeramiwe n’imiterere yabyo ifite agaciro mu bukungu. <ref name=":0">https://www.fws.gov/international/travel-and-trade/illegal-wildlife-trade.html</ref> Ubwoko nk'ubwo burimo inyamabere nini nini nk'inzovu zo muri Afurika, ingwe, n'inkura. [yacuruzaga ku [[:en:Ivory_trade|matako]], uruhu, n'amahembe bikurikiranye].  <ref>https://www.worldwildlife.org/threats/illegal-wildlife-trade</ref> Intego nke zizwi cyane zo guhiga zirimo gusarura ibihingwa bikingiwe ninyamaswa zo kwibuka, ibiryo, uruhu, amatungo, nibindi byinshi; Kuberako ba rushimusi bakunda kwibasira amoko yugarijwe kandi yangirika, guhiga bitera abaturage bake kugabanuka cyane. 

== Kwica Inyamaswa ==
Kwica ni ukwica nkana no guhitamo kwica inyamaswa za leta kubwimpamvu zitandukanye. Urugero rwibi ni ukwica inyoni, aho gahunda ya "control [[:en:Shark_culling|shark]] " muri [[:en:Queensland|Queensland]] na [[New South Whttps://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Queenslandales|New South Wales]] (muri [[Ositaraliya]] ) yahitanye ibihumbi n’ibihumbi, hamwe [[:en:Turtle|n’inyenzi]], [[:en:Dolphin|dolphine]], [[:en:Whale|balale]], n’ubuzima bwo mu nyanja . <ref name="afd_au">http://www.afd.org.au/news-articles/queenslands-shark-control-program-has-snagged-84000-animals</ref> <ref>https://web.archive.org/web/20181002102324/https://www.marineconservation.org.au/pages/shark-culling.html "Shark Culling". marineconservation.org.au. Archived from the original on 2018-10-02. Retrieved January 4, 2019.</ref> <ref>https://hsi.org.au/blog/2016/12/08/shark-nets-death-traps-for-marine-animals/  Morris, Jessica (December 8, 2016). "Shark Nets – Death Traps For Marine Animals". hsi.org.au. Retrieved January 4, 2019.</ref> Gahunda ya Queensland "shark control" yonyine yishe inyanja zigera ku 50.000 - yica kandi inyamaswa zo mu nyanja zirenga 84.000. <ref>https://www.news.com.au/technology/science/animals/aussie-shark-population-is-staggering-decline/news-story/49e910c828b6e2b735d1c68e6b2c956e ''Aussie Shark Population In Staggering Decline.'' NewsComAu. 14 December 2018. Retrieved September 4, 2019.</ref> <ref name="afd_au" /> Hariho kandi ingero z'abaturage bica muri Amerika, nka [[:en:Conservation_of_American_bison|bison muri Montana]] hamwe na swans, ingagi, n'impongo i New York n'ahandi. <ref>https://news.nationalgeographic.com/news/2014/03/140305-culling-badgers-deer-bison-swans-ethics-conservation/</ref> <ref name="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4693205/">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4693205</ref>

== Umwuka mubi ==
Ubwoko butandukanye [[:en:Pollutant|bwanduye]] bugira ingaruka mbi kubuzima bwibinyabuzima. Kubintu bimwe bihumanya, guhura byoroshye 
[[Dosiye:Deepwater_Horizon_Oil_Spill_-_Gulf_of_Mexico.jpg|alt=|thumb|275x275px|Kureba mu kirere BP Amazi ya Horizon yamenetse muri 2010.]]
birahagije kugirango byangiritse (urugero: imiti yica udukoko). Kubandi, binyuze mu guhumeka (urugero: imyuka ihumanya ikirere) cyangwa kuyifata (urugero ibyuma byuburozi). Umwanda uhindura amoko atandukanye muburyo butandukanye kuburyo umwanda mubi kuri umwe ushobora kutagira ingaruka kubindi.

* '''Ibyuka bihumanya ikirere''' : [[:en:Air_pollution|Ibyuka bihumanya ikirere]] bituruka ku gutwika ibicanwa n’ibisohoka mu nganda. Izi zigira ingaruka zitaziguye kandi zitaziguye ku buzima bwibinyabuzima ndetse nibidukikije. Kurugero, urugero rwinshi rwa okiside ya [[:en:Sulfur_oxide|sulfuru]] (SO <sub>x</sub> ) irashobora kwangiza ibimera no guhagarika imikurire yabyo. <ref>https://www.epa.gov/so2-pollution/sulfur-dioxide-basics</ref> Okiside ya sulfure nayo igira uruhare mu mvura ya aside, ikangiza urusobe rw’ibinyabuzima byo ku isi ndetse n’amazi. Ibindi bihumanya ikirere nka [[:en:Smog|umwotsi]], [[:en:Tropospheric_ozone|ozone yo ku butaka]], hamwe nuduce duto tugabanya ubwiza bwikirere.
* '''Ibyuma biremereye''' : Ibyuma biremereye nka [[:en:Arsenic_poisoning|arsenic]], [[:en:Lead_poisoning|gurş]], na [[:en:Mercury_poisoning|mercure]] mubisanzwe bibaho kurwego rwo hasi mubidukikije, ariko iyo byinjijwe mukigero kinini, birashobora kwangiza ingingo na kanseri. <ref>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:BookSources/9783764383398</ref> Ukuntu ari uburozi biterwa nicyuma nyacyo, ingano yatewe, ninyamaswa zayiriye. Ibikorwa byabantu nko gucukura, gushonga, gutwika ibicanwa, hamwe ninganda zitandukanye zagize uruhare mukuzamuka kwicyuma kiremereye mubidukikije.
* '''Imiti yuburozi''' : Hariho amasoko menshi yanduza imiti yubumara harimo amazi mabi yinganda, isuka ryamavuta, hamwe nudukoko twangiza. Hano hari imiti myinshi yubumara kuburyo hariho ningaruka nyinshi zingaruka zubuzima. Kurugero, imiti yica udukoko hamwe nudukoko tumwe na tumwe twinganda ni [[:en:Special:BookSources/9783764383398|imyanda ihumanya]] . Ibyo bihumanya biramba kandi birashobora gutera kanseri, indwara zimyororokere, ibibazo byumubiri, nibibazo bya sisitemu. <ref>https://www.who.int/foodsafety/areas_work/chemical-risks/pops/en/</ref>

== Imihindagurikire y’ibihe/climate change ==
Abantu bafite uruhare runini mu [[:en:Climate_change|ihindagurika ry’ikirere]] muri iki gihe rihindura ibidukikije ku isi. Bifitanye isano na bimwe mubyavuzwe haruguru bibangamira inyamanswa nko [[:en:Habitat_destruction|gusenya aho gutura]] no guhumana. Kwiyongera k'ubushyuhe, gushonga urubura, guhindura imiterere yimvura, [[:en:Drought|amapfa akomeye]], [[:en:Heat_wave|imivumba]] ikunze kugaragara, ubukana bwumuyaga, hamwe n’inyanja izamuka ni zimwe mu ngaruka z’imihindagurikire y’ikirere. <ref>https://climate.nasa.gov/effects</ref> Fenomena nk'amapfa, ubushyuhe, umuyaga mwinshi, hamwe [[:en:Sea_level_rise|n'izamuka ry'inyanja]], biganisha ku gusenya aho gutuye. Hagati aho, ikirere gishyuha, imvura ihindagurika, n’imihindagurikire y’ikirere bizagira ingaruka ku bwoko. Muri rusange, ingaruka z’imihindagurikire y’ikirere zongera ibibazo ku binyabuzima, kandi amoko adashobora guhangana n’imihindagurikire yihuse azashira. <ref>https://doi.org/10.1126%2Fscience.1200303</ref> Mu gihe imihindagurikire y’ikirere igezweho iterwa n’abantu, [[:en:Paleoclimatology|ibihe by’imihindagurikire y’ikirere]] byabayeho bisanzwe bituma abantu barimbuka. 

== Kubungabunga ubwoko Bwinyamanswa ==
[[Dosiye:Leatherback_Sea_Turtle_(17665415746).jpg|thumb|275x275px|Inyenzi zo mu nyanja ( ''Dermochelys coriacea'' )]]


Bigereranijwe ko, kubera ibikorwa byabantu, ibipimo byokuzimangana kurubu bikubye inshuro 1000 kurenza igipimo cyo [[:en:Background_extinction_rate|kuzimangana (igipimo]] gisanzwe cyo kuzimangana kibaho nta ngaruka zindi). <ref>https://doi.org/10.1126%2Fscience.1246752</ref> Nk’uko [[:en:IUCN_Red_List|IUCN]] ibigaragaza, mu moko yose yasuzumwe, abarenga 27.000 bafite ibyago byo kuzimira kandi bagomba kubungabungwa. <ref name=":42">https://www.iucnredlist.org/en</ref> Muri byo, 25% ni inyamaswa z’inyamabere, 14% ni inyoni, naho 40% ni amphibian. <ref name=":42" /> Ariko, kubera ko amoko yose atigeze asuzumwa, iyo mibare irashobora kuba myinshi. Raporo y’umuryango w’abibumbye yo mu mwaka wa 2019 isuzuma ibinyabuzima bitandukanye ku isi ikwirakwiza amakuru ya IUCN ku moko yose kandi igereranya ko miliyoni imwe ku isi ishobora kuzimira. <ref>https://www.un.org/sustainabledevelopment/blog/2019/05/nature-decline-unprecedented-report</ref> <ref>https://www.ipbes.net/system/tdf/spm_global_unedited_advance.pdf?file=1&type=node&id=35245</ref> Nyamara, kubera ko amikoro ari make, rimwe na rimwe ntibishoboka guha amoko yose akeneye kubungabungwa neza. Guhitamo amoko yo kubungabunga ni umurimo wukuntu hafi yo kuzimangana ubwoko, niba ubwoko ari ingenzi kubinyabuzima butuyemo, nuburyo tubyitayeho.  

== Kubungabunga ibidukikije /Habitat conservation ==
[[Dosiye:Red-cockaded_woodpecker_feeding_young_(5806270700).jpg|thumb|198x198px|Igiti gitukura ( ''Picoides borealis'' )]]
[[:en:Habitat_conservation|Kubungabunga]] imiturire nigikorwa cyo kurinda aho gutura <ref>https://www.thesamajh.in/Protect_WildLife_The_Samajh.aspx</ref> hagamijwe kurinda amoko arimo. <ref name=":123">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)</ref> Ibi rimwe na rimwe biba byiza kwibanda ku bwoko bumwe cyane cyane iyo ubwoko buvugwa bufite aho busaba cyane cyangwa bukaba butuye hamwe nandi moko menshi yangirika. Iyanyuma ikunze kugaragara kubinyabuzima bibera ahantu [[:en:Biodiversity_hotspot|hashyushye h’ibinyabuzima]], akaba ari uturere tw’isi dufite ubwinshi bw’ibinyabuzima byanduye (ubwoko butaboneka ahandi ku isi). <ref>https://doi.org/10.1038%2F35002501</ref> Byinshi muribi bishyushye biri mu turere dushyuha, cyane cyane amashyamba yo mu turere dushyuha nka Amazone. Kubungabunga imiturire mubisanzwe bikorwa mugushira ahantu harinzwe nka parike yigihugu cyangwa ibidukikije. Nubwo mugihe agace kadakozwe muri parike cyangwa kubigenewe, birashobora gukurikiranwa no kubungabungwa.

== Uburyo bwo kubungabunga ==

=== Gukurikirana inyamaswa zo mu gasozi ===
[[Dosiye:Asiatic_Wild_Dogs_(44187676292).jpg|thumb|Gukurikirana idahwitse ya [[Dhole|dhole ningirakamaro]] mubumenyi kubijyanye no kubungabunga ibidukikije. Ubushakashatsi burakenewe mubutayu bwubushinwa.]]
Gukurikirana ibinyabuzima by’inyamanswa nigice cyingenzi cyo kubungabunga ibidukikije kuko bituma abayobozi bakusanya amakuru ajyanye n’ibinyabuzima byugarije ndetse no gupima imikorere y’ingamba zo gucunga. Gukurikirana birashobora kuba hafi, uturere, cyangwa intera-mugari, kandi birashobora gushiramo umwe cyangwa benshi batandukanye. Ibipimo bikunze gukusanywa mugihe cyo gukurikirana harimo umubare wabaturage, ikwirakwizwa ry’akarere, hamwe nubwoko butandukanye, nubwo ibindi bipimo byinshi bishobora gukoreshwa. Uburyo bwo gukurikirana bushobora gushyirwa mubice nka "direct" cyangwa "indirect". Uburyo butaziguye bushingiye ku kubona cyangwa kumva inyamaswa mu buryo butaziguye, mu gihe uburyo butaziguye bushingira ku "bimenyetso" byerekana ko inyamaswa zihari. Ku binyabuzima byo ku isi, uburyo busanzwe bwo gukurikirana burimo kwitegereza bitaziguye, ibimenyetso-gufata, guhinduranya, hamwe nubushakashatsi bwibihinduka. Uburyo butaziguye burimo sitasiyo, kubara fecal, kuvanaho ibiryo, gufungura cyangwa gufunga ibifungura-gufungura, kubara, kubara, amakarita ya knockdown, inzira ya shelegi, cyangwa kwitabira guhamagara amajwi. <ref>https://pubag.nal.usda.gov/download/37910/PDF</ref>For large, terrestrial vertebrates, a popular method is to use camera traps for population estimation along with mark-recapture techniques. This method has been used successfully with tigers, black bears and numerous other species.<ref>https://link.springer.com/book/10.1007/978-981-10-5436-5?noAccess=true</ref><ref>https://doi.org/10.2192%2FURSU-D-16-00030.1</ref> [[:en:Remote_camera|Trail cameras]] can be triggered remotely and automatically via sound, infrared sensors, etc. [[:en:Computer_vision|Computer vision]]-based animal individual re-identification methods have been developed to automate such ''sight-resight'' calculations.<ref name="Schneider Taylor Kremer 2020 p.">https://doi.org/10.1109%2Fwacvw50321.2020.9096925</ref><ref name="Wang Ding Zhai Zhang 2021 pp. 1–1">https://ui.adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2021ITIP...30.2837W</ref> Mark-recapture methods are also used with genetic data from non-invasive hair or fecal samples.<ref>https://www.researchgate.net/publication/232679082</ref> Such information can be analyzed independently or in conjunction with photographic methods to get a more complete picture of population viability.

